Divine Purpose		KEY:Emotional Focus / Remorse ~ Divine Purpose			SORTKEY:Emotional Focus 2c	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Emotional Focus / Remorse.SpecialQuality				SOURCEPAGE:p.19	DESC:A fated guide’s phantom gains Deific Obedience as a bonus feat, though the spiritualist must obey her god’s obedience to gain any benefit.		ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Deific Obedience
Long-Suffering Strike	KEY:Emotional Focus / Remorse ~ Long-Suffering Strike		SORTKEY:Emotional Focus 2d	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Emotional Focus / Remorse.SpecialQuality.Supernatural		SOURCEPAGE:p.19	DESC:When a phantom with this focus hits a creature with its slam attack, that creature must succeed at a Will saving throw (DC %1) or any attacks targeting the creature gain a +1 bonus on their attack rolls and damage rolls until the beginning of the phantom’s next turn. Penalties from multiple hits don’t stack with themselves.|10+HD/2+CHA
Aura of Regret		KEY:Emotional Focus / Remorse ~ Aura of Regret			SORTKEY:Emotional Focus 2e	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Emotional Focus / Remorse.SpecialQuality.Supernatural		SOURCEPAGE:p.19	DESC:When the spiritualist reaches 7th level, her phantom can emit a 10-foot-radius aura of regret as a swift action. Enemies within the aura take a –2 penalty on skill checks, on caster level checks, on combat maneuver checks, and to CMD. Ending the aura is a free action. The phantom can use this ability in either ectoplasmic or incorporeal form.
Keening			KEY:Emotional Focus / Remorse ~ Keening				SORTKEY:Emotional Focus 2f	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Emotional Focus / Remorse.SpecialQuality.Supernatural		SOURCEPAGE:p.19	DESC:When the spiritualist reaches 12th level, her phantom can wail about its misdeeds once per day as a standard action, affecting all creatures within a 30-foot cone with the terrible remorse (UM) spell. The phantom uses its Hit Dice as its caster level for the effect, and the DC equals %1. The phantom can use this ability in either ectoplasmic or incorporeal form.|10+HD/2+CHA
Utter Misery		KEY:Emotional Focus / Remorse ~ Utter Misery			SORTKEY:Emotional Focus 2g	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Emotional Focus / Remorse.SpecialQuality.Supernatural		SOURCEPAGE:p.19	DESC:When the spiritualist reaches 17th level, her phantom’s long-suffering strike also causes a creature that fails its save to become stunned until the beginning of the phantom’s next turn.
